Title: Should we trust the World Health Organization? It's all about the science isn't it.
Thesis: Are there any smokings guns about this NGO having been compromized by corporate interests?
Conclusion:
- Philanthropist-Investor extraordinaire Bill Gates and other smarter and less visible globalists are funding the WHO and at the same time investing in Big Pharma and vaccines.
- The WHO is then declaring dubious pandemics with wildly different outcomes. From the barely noticable swine flu of 2010 to the unprecedented Covid19 that has shifted the entire world to a technocratic dystopia.
- As a result the philanthropist-investors are making a killing and the pandemic has resulted in the biggest wealth shift in history.

Piece.Title: How is the World Health Organization funded?
Piece.Thesis:
In their own website they answer this for us. 
- The membership fee of countries accounts for less than a quarter of the financing.
- "Voluntary contributions" make up the bulk of it, and it comes from intergovernmental organizations and "philanthropic foundations". Who could that be?

Piece.Title: Has the WHO declared any other pandemics the last few years?
Piece.Thesis: So according to WHO, there was a swine flu H1N1 pandemic that came and went in 2009-2010 and the world barely noticed. But the Covid 19 pandemic was such a threat for humanity that the whole world had to descent to totallitarianism within two years. How are these both a "pandemic" if the response was so vastly different. Could the previous pandemics have been a dry run for a world take over by globalists?
